| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4735 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c1ad0753-b412-57fd-9c58-9a8260198697"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
